name: Variation II on Beethoven's Symphony No.9 Op.125
description:
A sample taken from Beethoven's Symphony No.9 Finale is modulated in frequency with itself. Improvisation of frequency changes played with a Pure Data instrument and an AKAI LPD8 MIDI controller.

Original Public Domain recording can be found here https://imslp.org/wiki/Special:ReverseLookup/516415
